START

Create empty student list

Display menu:
    1. Add Student
    2. View Students
    3. Search Student
    4. Delete Student
    5. Exit

IF user selects Add Student
    Ask user for student information
    Store information in dictionary
    Add dictionary to list

IF user selects View Students
    Display all students

IF user selects Search Student
    Ask for Student ID
    Find matching student
    Display student information

IF user selects Delete Student
    Ask for Student ID
    Remove matching student

IF user selects Exit
    End program

STOP
